extends layout

block content
  .home-hero
    .container
      .home-hero-badge Educational Tool
      h1.home-hero-title Blockchain Demo
      p.home-hero-subtitle
        | An interactive, step-by-step visualization of how a blockchain works —
        | from hashing a single value to a fully distributed ledger.
      p.home-hero-meta
        | Designed for classroom use &middot; Universidad Alfonso X el Sabio &middot; Cryptography

  .container.home-modules
    .row
      .col-sm-6.col-md-4
        a.home-card(href='/hash')
          .home-card-icon
            span.glyphicon.glyphicon-lock
          h3 Hash Function
          p
            | Type any text and see its SHA-256 digest update in real time.
            | Understand why even a single character change produces a completely different hash.
      .col-sm-6.col-md-4
        a.home-card(href='/block')
          .home-card-icon
            span.glyphicon.glyphicon-th-large
          h3 Block
          p
            | Add a nonce to the data and mine until the hash meets the required difficulty target
            | (leading zeros). See Proof-of-Work in action.
      .col-sm-6.col-md-4
        a.home-card(href='/blockchain')
          .home-card-icon
            span.glyphicon.glyphicon-link
          h3 Blockchain
          p
            | Chain blocks together using each block&rsquo;s hash as the previous block pointer.
            | Tamper with one block and watch the entire chain break.
      .col-sm-6.col-md-4
        a.home-card(href='/distributed')
          .home-card-icon
            span.glyphicon.glyphicon-globe
          h3 Distributed
          p
            | Replicate the chain across multiple peers. Modify one peer&rsquo;s data and see
            | how the network detects and rejects the tampered copy.
      .col-sm-6.col-md-4
        a.home-card(href='/tokens')
          .home-card-icon
            span.glyphicon.glyphicon-transfer
          h3 Tokens
          p
            | Replace raw data with financial transactions. See how a blockchain
            | records who sends how much to whom without a central bank.
      .col-sm-6.col-md-4
        a.home-card(href='/coinbase')
          .home-card-icon
            span.glyphicon.glyphicon-star
          h3 Coinbase
          p
            | Add a special coinbase transaction that creates new coins from nothing —
            | the mechanism by which miners are rewarded.

  .container
    p.home-attribution
      | Original demo by&nbsp;
      a(href='http://andersbrownworth.com/') Anders Brownworth
      | &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;
      a(href='https://github.com/anders94/blockchain-demo/') Source on GitHub
